text: Magnus Haraldsson may refer to: * Maccus mac Arailt (fl. 971–974), King of the Isles, also known as Magnus Haraldsson * Magnus II of Norway (1048–1069), King of Norway, also known as Magnus Haraldsson * Magnus Haraldsson of Norway (c. 1135 – c. 1145), King of Norway * Magnus Haraldsson (bishop of Skara), 1522–1529, see Diocese of Skara#History
title: Magnus Haraldsson
